Michael and Nikita agree on p is the next prime after 2^127-1
Michael decides secret m and sends Mod(2,p)^m is 89646952373925749567894332598989134553
Nikita secret n is 123456 so
Mod(2,p)^n = 158950970901130875643663016511694449147

#Determine p
p = next_probable_prime((2^127) - 1)
print p

170141183460469231731687303715884105757

#Use Michael's sent number and n to determine secret number
sent = 89646952373925749567894332598989134553
n = 123456
secret = Mod(sent, p)^n
print secret

79067655658429219567805855344438774741
#This is the secret number Michael and Nikita decided on
